CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 24, 1960, pg.19 reads: "Well-Known Guests - Among the thousands of people who took part in picnic at Pappy Day's Farm last Sunday, where winners of the Bartenders and Waitresses Contest received awards, were well known people shown above. They are, left to right: William (Popeye) Batts, Lucille McPherson, Al Johnson, Renna Johnson, Thomas Goode, Eleanor Goode -Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, left to right: Lucille McPhierson, William (Popeye) Batts, Al Johnson, Renna Johnson, Thomas Goode, and Eleanor Goode, gathered at the bar at Pappy Day's Farm picnic
